title: [1508521049] Mulled Wine with Dried Nuts - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon Ramsay prepares a warming jug of aromatic mulled wine with spiced nuts on the side. Perfect for when guests drop round. Subscribe for weekly videos. 

The most delicious Christmas recipes, cooked up by the world's greatest chef at home, Gordon Ramsay's Ultimate Christmas will teach you everything you need to know to cook up the perfect Christmas.


The official YouTube channel for Gordon Ramsay, with exclusive clips from a selection shows including Cookalong Live, Gordon's Great Escape and more. Subscribe for weekly videos.
